1. Put this directory as $HOME/bin/etc/tmux (or change relevant paths in scripts).
2. Link or copy tm script into $HOME/bin.\
3. Copy tmux.conf to $HOME/.tmux.conf (with a dot!).
4. Optionally add this alias into $HOME/.bashrc
        alias tml='tm -l'
5. Run tmux with tm script, using either one of pre-configured sessions or
   named default session or anonymous default session.
